<H3><CENTER><font color="#2F4F2F">"MATTERS OF CONSEQUENCE"</font color="#2F4F2F">
<BR>
<A HREF="jpnote.htm">EDITORIAL</A><BR>
by Jane Wardlow Prettyman, Editor<BR>
The Real News Page</CENTER>
<P>
<HR width=100%>
<PRE>   </PRE>

<CENTER><IMG SRC="salonsml.gif"> <BR>
