<DOCNO>WT27-B08-161</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA002-000019-B006-166</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.rain.org:80/~openmind/lyons.htm 198.68.144.2 19970101121120 text/html 5044
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Wed, 01 Jan 1997 12:09:08 GMT
