<DOCOLDNO>IA002-000019-B033-152</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.rain.org:80/~openmind/tabmind.htm 198.68.144.2 19970101114350 text/html 7224
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
